name: Moroccan Caftan
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

You have embarked into a vacation and your plane just landed at your destination, you hear a bell ringing and your pilot starts speaking

"Ladies and gentlemen,

Welcome to Morocco, North-Africa.

I sincerely hope you will enjoy your stay, enjoy the sun, beaches, mountains, culture, and especially the food.
If I may give you a recommendation, please do stop by the artisans' district and buy a caftan dress. This piece of cultural clothing is internationally renowned. Besides Morocco recently applied for the caftan to be recognized as a piece of World Heritage by UNESCO. Do not miss the opportunity to get a caftan for you or your significant other!"

---

I sincerely hope you will enjoy using this LoRA as much as I enjoyed making it. As you can see the results are beautiful and the model is very versatile and can be used in many styles.

Go ahead, use it, have fun, and make me proud of introducing you to the culture of caftan!
